    "description": "We at Intel India Digital Technologies are looking for an experienced Senior Software Engineer based out of Kolkata. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Intel India Digital Technologies:\nIntel India Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kolkata, West Bengal, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Intel India Digital Technologies!",
